DOW’S 1960 VINTAGE PORT

We offer a wine miracle—a True Vintage Port of the great, historic 1960 vintage made exclusively from the grapes of that extraordinary year. England is the home of vintage Port—this DOW’S 1960 was bottled in England in 1962 within two years of the vintage in Portugal. It is possibly the best vintage Port you have ever tasted. It normally sells for over $20 the bottle. Quantity is limited—we urge phoning almost immediately to get some. On sale at $9.75 bottle, $113.50 case.
